Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.28,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}不是勇者也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:47.87,Dragner opchgb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}只要能守护住你一人的话
